cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the problem of image classification using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and specifically focuses on the medical image dataset. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of pre-trained networks and transfer learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the retrieval and classification accuracy, which could fall under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
